<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Service Hub</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --page-bg:
        radial-gradient(circle at 12% 18%, rgba(255, 179, 71, 0.22), transparent 26%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 88% 14%, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.18), transparent 24%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 78% 82%, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.16), transparent 24%),
        linear-gradient(160deg, #f9f4ea 0%, #eef6ff 46%, #f1fbf6 100%);
      --surface: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      --surface-strong: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      --border: rgba(24, 39, 75, 0.1);
      --text: #163047;
      --muted: #5f7184;
      --primary: #e76f51;
      --primary-dark: #c85236;
      --secondary: #1d4ed8;
      --success: #159a6f;
      --shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.12);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      /* background: var(--page-bg); */
      background-color:  #f9f4ea;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .page {
      width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 28px 0 40px;
    }

    .hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
      align-items: stretch;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .heroCard,
    .infoCard,
    .serviceCard {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 28px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }

    .heroCard {
      padding: 34px;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(231, 111, 81, 0.12);
      color: var(--primary-dark);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4vw, 4.8rem);
      line-height: 0.94;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .subtitle {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 18px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .heroActions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .cta,
    .linkBtn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 52px;
      padding: 0 20px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: transform 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease, background 0.18s ease;
    }

    .cta {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #fff;
      /* box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(231, 111, 81, 0.28); */
    }

    .linkBtn {
      background: rgba(29, 78, 216, 0.1);
      color: var(--secondary);
    }

    .cta:hover,
    .linkBtn:hover,
    .serviceCard:hover {
      transform: rotate(15deg);
    }

    .infoCard {
      padding: 24px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
      display: none;
    }

    .statusBox {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(29, 78, 216, 0.12), rgba(21, 154, 111, 0.12));
    }

    .statusBox strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .statusBox p,
    .miniList p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .miniList {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .miniItem {
      padding: 16px 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: var(--surface-strong);
      border: 1px solid rgba(24, 39, 75, 0.08);
    }

    .miniItem strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .servicesHeader {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: end;
      gap: 16px;
      margin: 10px 0 18px;
    }

    .servicesHeader h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2.6vw, 2.3rem);
    }

    .servicesHeader p {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 620px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .serviceGrid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .serviceCard {
      padding: 22px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
      transition: transform 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease;
    }

    .serviceTop {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: start;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .serviceCard h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.28rem;
    }

    .tag {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(21, 154, 111, 0.12);
      color: var(--success);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .serviceCard p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .points {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .point {
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(243, 247, 252, 0.9);
      border: 1px solid rgba(24, 39, 75, 0.06);
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .serviceActions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: auto;
    }

    .serviceActions a {
      flex: 1 1 180px;
    }

    .footerNote {
      margin-top: 24px;
      padding: 18px 22px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .hero,
      .serviceGrid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .servicesHeader {
        align-items: start;
        flex-direction: column;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .page {
        width: min(100% - 20px, 1180px);
        padding-top: 16px;
        padding-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .heroCard,
      .infoCard,
      .serviceCard {
        border-radius: 22px;
      }

      .heroCard,
      .infoCard,
      .serviceCard,
      .footerNote {
        padding-left: 18px;
        padding-right: 18px;
      }

      .heroCard {
        padding-top: 24px;
        padding-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .serviceTop {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .heroActions,
      .serviceActions {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .serviceActions a {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="page">
    <section class="hero">
      <article class="heroCard">
        <p class="eyebrow">Main Home Page</p>
        <h1>One clean place to open every service you built.</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
          This dashboard gives you a simple starting point for your apps. Open any service in one click,
          move easily between tools, and use the same homepage on desktop or mobile.
        </p>
        <div class="heroActions">
          <a class="cta" href="<%= services[0].path %>">Open First Service</a>
          <a class="linkBtn" href="#services">Browse All Services</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <aside class="infoCard">
        <div class="statusBox">
          <strong>Your Workspace Hub</strong>
          <p>Use this as the main landing page for your AI tools, ML tools, and future services.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="miniList">
          <div class="miniItem">
            <strong>Responsive Layout</strong>
            <p>The cards stack nicely on smaller screens so the homepage stays easy to use everywhere.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="miniItem">
            <strong>Fast Navigation</strong>
            <p>Each service card includes a clear action button so you can jump directly into the tool you want.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="miniItem">
            <strong>Ready To Grow</strong>
            <p>You can add more services later by extending the `services` array in your server route.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section id="services">
      <div class="servicesHeader">
        <div>
          <h2>Available Services</h2>
          <p>Choose the service you want to use right now. Each card is focused, readable, and built for quick access.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="serviceGrid">
        <% services.forEach((service) => { %>
          <article class="serviceCard">
            <div class="serviceTop">
              <div>
                <h3><%= service.name %></h3>
              </div>
              <span class="tag"><%= service.tag %></span>
            </div>

            <p><%= service.description %></p>

            <div class="points">
              <% service.bullets.forEach((item) => { %>
                <div class="point"><%= item %></div>
              <% }) %>
            </div>

            <div class="serviceActions">
              <a class="cta" href="<%= service.path %>">Open Service</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        <% }) %>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="footerNote">
      This page is now your main entry point at <strong>`/`</strong>. Your existing service routes still work,
      but the homepage gives you one simple place to reach all of them.
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
